## Files Modified
- `package-lock.json` - Updated from running `npm install` to ensure dependencies are current

## No Code Changes Required

The project already has Vercel Web Analytics properly configured according to the official documentation. The implementation follows React best practices by:
- Using the framework-specific import path (`@vercel/analytics/react`)
- Placing the Analytics component at the app root level
- Using the self-closing tag syntax `<Analytics />`

The analytics will automatically track page views and web vitals once the application is deployed to Vercel with Analytics enabled in the project dashboard.
